
emqttd_dashboard
================

Dashboard for emqttd broker.

Build
------

make && make ct

Configurtion
------------

.. code::

    [
      {emqttd_dashboard, [
        {listener, 
            {emqttd_dashboard, 18083, [
                {acceptors, 4},
                {max_clients, 512}]}}
      ]}
    ].

Load Plugin
-----------

```
./bin/emqttd_ctl plugins load emqttd_dashboard
```

Login
-----

URL: http://host:18083

Username: admin

Password: public (admin before 0.10.4)

